; Coverage for history.cc: price map lookup with multiple price points
; Tests upper_bound selection and time-based price filtering
; The most recent price at evaluation time ($1.20 from 2024/04/01) is used

P 2024/01/01 EUR $1.10
P 2024/02/01 EUR $1.15
P 2024/03/01 EUR $1.08
P 2024/04/01 EUR $1.20

2024/01/15 Trip 1
    Expenses:Travel    100 EUR
    Assets:Checking

2024/03/15 Trip 2
    Expenses:Travel    200 EUR
    Assets:Checking

test bal --market --exchange '$' --now 2024/05/01 Expenses
             $360.00  Expenses:Travel
end test
